extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em Inventory], a very basic Express website

  h1 Content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The inventory has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Items:] !{data.item_count}
      li #[strong Manufacturers:] !{data.manufacturer_count}
      li #[strong Categories:] !{data.category_count}